('4af9bebf-5bc0-4c6e-9957-1064bb1aea99', 'Chemicon', '<p>\r\n	With infinite research potential and limitless boundaries, the chemical branch of science is fast becoming one of the most sought after fields in the modern age, primarily due to its versatility and applicability in many prominent issues facing our predominantly industry-based civilization. With a range of events designed to test your ability to create, adapt, innovate, design, apply and invent, the Chemical events emphasize on participants ability to combine effective design with creativity, all the while requiring a very solid foundation on the phenomena each event is based on.</p>\r\n', 'chemical', ''),
('4af9bedd-cd34-47ed-8dcc-1064bb1aea99', 'Corporate', '<p>\r\n	The corporate world has always held an allure for those who enjoy taking up challenges and risks with the final aim being the next multibillionaire. This category is for those who enjoy the high stakes- high reward system and are gifted with an uncanny ability to interpret numbers. With events that are designed to assess your analytical mind; it is going to be the ultimate contest to see who has the aptitude to be among the future Fortune 500.</p>\r\n', 'corporate', ''),
('4af9dcf3-b600-4454-8326-1064bb1aea99', 'Spark (Electronics)', '<p>\r\n	<em><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">To view the Official Spark 2011 Poster, click</span> <a href="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/img/uploads/Spark_V3.jpg" target="Poster">here</a><br />\r\n	</strong></em></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><br />\r\n	</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>In Association With</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<a href="http://www.bits-goa.ac.in/Departments/Electronics/IEEE/index.html"><img alt="" height="100" src="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/img/uploads/IEEE_logo.png" width="200" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<a href="http://www.bits-goa.ac.in/Departments/Electronics/IEEE/index.html" target="_blank"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Student Branch BITS Pilani K. K. Birla Goa Campus</strong></span></span><br />\r\n	</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	For the electronic enthusiast in you,<strong>Spark</strong> presents a plethora of events...As someone wisely said,&quot;The new rules of Electronics - Build it and plug it - If it sparks, unplug it - If it smokes, turn it off - If it heats up, check it, and plug it back - Don&#39;t be afraid of trying something new.&quot;... Come design and discover...</p>\r\n', 'Spark', ''),
('4af9dd07-f94c-42fb-ad6d-1064bb1aea99', 'Mechagi', '<p>\r\n	The wheels of the mechanical world make one revolution after another, in more than just the literal sense. As the scientific world strives for innovation and efficiency, core engineering concepts take centre stage as top mechanical engineers and enthusiasts battle it out for technical glory.<br />\r\n	At Quark 2011, Mechagi will test your engineering skill to the limit &ndash; are you geared up for the challenge?</p>\r\n', 'mechagi', ''),
('4af9dd24-57f4-4ba4-aad7-1064bb1aea99', 'Programmers'' Inc', '<p>\r\n	The cyber world is all around us, ever evolving, ever changing. Programmers&#39; Inc, the series of events in Quark 2011 related to the cyberspace, ensure that you get the opportunity to be the agents of this change. Programmers&#39; Inc promises to not only be breathtaking in its simplicity and its knowledge, but also a source for the best Tech minds of the country to compete in a forum that is truly fitting to the genius of today&rsquo;s tech-savvy youth.</p>\r\n', 'programmers_inc', ''),
('4af9dd54-68fc-4cdf-b8da-1064bb1aea99', 'Roboficial', '<p>\r\n	&ldquo;<strong>Tomorrow belongs to those who conceive it today</strong>.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Quark becomes the Mecca of mechatronics with the robotics events offering the perfect blend of entertainment and technology. So, go ahead, and gear up for the ultimate showdown in design as you simulate a daunting wrestling match, or instead, skilfully create a cyborg that can rescue the last of the human species. Massive crowds, great rewards, and primarily &ndash; innovation at its supreme: This is your chance to make the future happen, now.</p>\r\n', 'roboficial', ''),
('4af9dd68-4c24-4a0b-b772-1064bb1aea99', 'Elixir', '<p>\r\n	Hosting events in the pure sciences - Physics, Chemistry, Biology and Mathematics - Elixir offers the young scientist an opportunity to thrive in fascinating events. Dabble with chemistry to solve everyday life problems. Let the physicist in you define a new world. Use mathematics to solve crime.</p>\r\n', 'elixir', ''),
('4af9dd7b-f494-45ee-9ab5-1064bb1aea99', 'Specials', '<p>\r\n	&ldquo;Always remember that you are unique. Just like everybody else.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Forming the silver lining of the cloud called Quark, the annual techno-managerial festival of BITS-Pilani, K.K. Birla Goa Campus, are the Specials that skim off the cream of talent of the country. Encompassing the no-holds-barred Quark Open Showcase Event, Matka, Paper Presentation and School Bag, the Specials amalgamate thrill, adventure, hobby, innovation, imagination and a tempting bouquet of prizes in a &lsquo;special&rsquo; way forming the highlight of the festival.</p>\r\n', 'specials', ''),
('4af9dd89-e1c0-48e3-9ab7-1064bb1aea99', 'Miscellaneous', '<p>\r\n	After your brain is exhausted, its finally time for your entertainment.... An assortment of fun filled events await to re-energize you!</p>\r\n', 'miscellaneous', ''),
('4cd98ece-6040-446e-aaaf-3744bb1aea99', 'Initiatives', '<!-- AddThis Button BEGIN --><!--<a class="addthis_button" href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?v=250&amp;username=deppstats" style="border: 0;"><img src="http://s7.addthis.com/static/btn/v2/lg-share-en.gif" width="125" height="16" alt="Bookmark and Share" style="border:0"/></a><script type="text/javascript" src="http://s7.addthis.com/js/250/addthis_widget.js#username=deppstats"></script>--><!-- AddThis Button END -->\r\n<p>\r\n	The world as we see now isn&#39;t just the product of actions but inactions!<br />\r\n	It&#39;s high time that we not only pay for our actions...but also inactions...<br />\r\n	Climate - society - people... where do we start!!<br />\r\n	<strong>Indulge. Innovate. Inspire.<br />\r\n	The change you wish to see...<br />\r\n	</strong><br />\r\n	With a vision of developing the future generation of change-makers, Quark 2011 presents you with the initiatives that directly target the chronic problems of the society today. In this segment of events, Quark 2011 focuses on sectors like Clean Energy, Green Buildings, Agricultural Efficiency, Rural Electrification and Urban Waste Management.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	This initiative will provide a perfect platform for the participants, professionals and policy makers to come together and deliberate on the solutions to these concerns. It also creates an ideal environment for spreading awareness about the development sector and usage of clean and efficient energy. It promotes as well as supports organizing guest lectures, conferences, workshops etc. encapsulated under the scope of the panel.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The initiatives include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Guest lectures on sustainability, environment and energy consumption.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Environmental exhibitions</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Performances by &quot;green&quot; musicians and bands</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	The initiatives also include three events; namely Bhagirath, Gangreen and Eco-Architect. Each of these events has been planned in association with actively functioning student bodies of the campus focusing on the related issues.</p>\r\n', 'initiatives', ''),
('4cd9979d-436c-43a1-a830-4ea4bb1aea99', 'Online Events', '<p>\r\n	<a href="http://idasystems.net/" target="_blank"><img alt="Ida Systems" height="91" src="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/img/uploads/IDALogo.jpg" width="150" /></a></p>\r\n', 'online_events', '');
