ents have a main STATEMENT and a BONUS statement, both the statements have equal weightage.</span></li>\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;">\r\n		<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">The breakup of evaluation is as follows:</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 0.75in;">\r\n	<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif''; font-size: 10pt;"><span>1.<span style="font: 7pt ''times new roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">Originality: 25%</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 0.75in;">\r\n	<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif''; font-size: 10pt;"><span>2.<span style="font: 7pt ''times new roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">Technical Ingenuity: 15%</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 0.75in;">\r\n	<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif''; font-size: 10pt;"><span>3.<span style="font: 7pt ''times new roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">Innovation: 20%</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 0.75in;">\r\n	<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif''; font-size: 10pt;"><span>4.<span style="font: 7pt ''times new roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">Social and Cultural acceptability: 10%</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 0.75in;">\r\n	<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif''; font-size: 10pt;"><span>5.<span style="font: 7pt ''times new roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">Feasibility: 30%</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;">\r\n		<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">The concept should be World Ready (Just a step away from real world implementation!)</span></li>\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;">\r\n		<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">There will be industry leaders, social scientists and eminent professors judging the event and their decision will be final.</span></li>\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;">\r\n		<span style="font-family: ''arial'',''sans-serif'';">The individual expectations of the problem statements are put up in the Problem Statements&rsquo; file itself!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<a href="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/files/Bhagirath-Quark2011.zip">CLICK HERE</a> for more information on each topic in the event!</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	If you have any query, please send an e-mail to <strong>bhagirath@bits-quark.org</strong>, or get in touch with any one of us:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Kunjan Gandhi</strong><br />\r\n	+91 9004040626</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Fatima Dilruba </strong><br />\r\n	+91 9637423618</p>\r\n', 1, 4);
