('4cd91ba9-9dac-475f-bf27-6210bb1aea99', 'Participation', '<p>\r\n	Haven&#39;t received the Quark 2011 poster package? <br />\r\n	Download the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/img/uploads/Quark2011Poster-LowRes.jpg " target="_blank">Quark 2011 poster</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Need an official invite for Quark 2011? <br />\r\n	Download the <a href="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/files/Quark2011Invite1.pdf " target="_blank">Quark 2011 Invite<br />\r\n	</a></p>\r\n', 'Other', 'participation', ''),
('4d36c3a2-4e08-4fe5-bf89-7564bb1aea99', 'Fractal Show', '<p>\r\n	<img align="right" alt="Fractals Image" height="267" src="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/img/uploads/fractals1.jpg " style="width: 288px; height: 176px" width="497" /><span style="font-size: 14px">By</span><span style="font-size: 16px"> <strong>Dr.Jonathan Wolfe</strong>,<em>New Mexico</em></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	This edition of Quark-2011, privileged to witness Dr. Jonathan Wolfe, Executive Director of Fractal Foundation,New Mexico, on the dais, presents to you, a guest lecture on 3D Fractal Zooms. Dr. Wolfe will delve into the intricacies of the concepts involved and show involved applications of fractals, such as in electrical engineering with fractal antenna.<br />\r\n	The presentation on the fascinating world of fractals will be adorned by an animated content of 3D Fractal Zooms promises to delight and dazzle the audiences.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Also you can be a part of an exclusive workshop with a hands-on session on how to use fractals organized by Dr. Wolfe&nbsp;and explore the Sierpinski Triangle Fractal that will&nbsp;inspire interest in math and sciences. <br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	For more details of the workshop, <a href="http://www.bits-quark.org/portal/fractals_workshop">click here</a>. <br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Read more about the <a href="http://fractalfoundation.org/">Fractal Foundation<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	</a>To know more about Fractals and its applications, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fractal#Applications" target="_blank">click here. </a></p>\r\n', 'Other', 'jonathan_fractals', ''),
('4d47c229-7fa8-42d4-aa11-15b0bb1aea99', 'Metalmate''s Exhibition Robots', '<p>\r\n	<span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 17px; "><u><strong>Metalmate&#39;s Exhibition Robots</strong></u></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Metalmate Inc. , a pioneer in marketing a wide range of Commercial Robotics products in India, brings to you a plethora of Robots, high on Entertainment and Innovation. &nbsp;We specialize in creating Commercial Robot Entertainment &amp; Promotional Zones and conducting innovative Mini-Robot-Building Workshops based on Alternate Energy, Mechanics and various forms of Locomotion for Amateurs, Learners &amp; Experts alike!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Today, Exhibiton &amp; Entertainment Robotics is an area of increasing interest, investment, and hype. When we say &quot;ROBOTIC&quot; we do not mean a &#39;regular fully automatic product&#39;, what we mean is a &#39;Intelligent autonomous interactive machine with a brain of its own&#39;. Bill Gates calls them &quot;The Next Big Thing&quot;! The prevailing wisdom is that the personal robots market resembles the personal computer market of the mid-1970s and their function may be to perform a task, to act as a security system, to entertain people, or to be used as an educational and promotional tool. &nbsp;Metalmate Inc. is a pioneer in marketing a wide range of personal Robotic products, Exhibition Robots &amp; Robot toys in India. When not entertaining people, you can see our Robots promoting various brands and products at leading trade fairs, exhibitions &amp; conferences around the country!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	At our Quark 2011 exhibit, you will find yourself entertained by</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Three Sophisticated Female Robots , as your Hosts distributing promotional material to the crowd and blowing kisses to whoever seems interested!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Mobile Surveillance Robot in its full form taking live videos of the crowd around it! Touted to be the most advanced mobile webcam in the market today, it is a WiFi remote controlled patrolling surveillance robot that can be controlled by any device with a web browser, even web enabled cell phones ; One can check on your home or office from anywhere a web connection exists. It automatically returns to his docking station to recharge. What else!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Gaming Robot Roboni-i is a fully programmable Robot with sensors that make it aware of its environment and that enable it to interact with other robots. Unique wheel design uses two loops (hoops or rings) to propel the robot.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Robotic Ant Bug : High-speed robotic creature that reacts to touch that races forward until it encounters an obstacle and then races backward..</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Robotic Crab Bug: The Crab, the autonomous robotic creature that hides in the dark, the crab will hide in shaded areas until a loud sound or exposure to light chases out in to the open. The crab will change direction automatically in pre- programmed intervals or in reaction to loud sounds.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Robotic Nano Bug: A Nano bug flips over by itself, skitters around on any smooth surface, moves away from any obstacles. These little critters act just like real bugs!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Micro Robotic Creature: This fully autonomous robot will scurry along until it encounters an obstacle or hears a loud sound and then back up and move in a different direction..</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Robotic Inchworm Bug: The Inchworm Robot is the first full-range control robotic creature in the Hexbug lineup, and has dual control which allows you to control two separate Inchworms at the same time and much more..</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Mini Performing Robot, Male Robot, Chatterbot, Pet Care Robots and many more.....</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	At Metalmate, You will often hear us say, We Welcome You To The Future!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Get more information: <a href="http://www.metalmateinc.com">www.metalmateinc.com</a></p>\r\n', 'Other', 'metalmate_exhibitions', ''),
('4d49020e-31a4-4f12-8d77-5f19bb1aea99', 'ISRO Lecture', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="Apple-style-span"><strong>Satellite Navigation</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="Apple-style-span">Mr. Vilas Palsule</span></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">ISRO Ahmedabad Director(DECU)</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; "><br />\r\n		</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; ">Venue &amp; Time: CC 117 3rd Feb 11:00 PM</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; "><br />\r\n		</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; ">Mr. Vilas Palsule is the Director of ISRO-Ahmedabad DECU(Development and Educational Communication Unit) division. He&nbsp;is also the Associate Project Director of EDUSAT. He&nbsp;has been&nbsp;instrumental in the success, Tele- Medicine Project by ISRO and&nbsp; the Gramsat Program.</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; "><br />\r\n		</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; ">He is assigned with the prime responsibility for providing configurations for all EDUSAT networks in the country and to develop new and state of art low cast multi media distance education networks using DVS-RCS technology.</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; "><br />\r\n		</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; ">Presently he is heading an Advanced Communication Technology Division at SAC and working in the field of Geo-Mobile communication , Multi-media distance education systems , Encryption , Navigational receivers (GNSS) and Power - bandwidth Efficient higher order modulation techniques. He is also assigned with the responsibility of developing all critical technologies of ground and payload for IRNSS as an APD IRNSS.He was responsible for developing various spread spectrum systems, first of its kind in India, under Apple Utilization Project.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Other', 'isro_lecture', '');
